spells.description: Equip: Your spells have a chance to charge the device and request a Backfill Barrel near your target's location. Damaging the barrel causes it to explode, inflicting 868,611 Fire damage split between nearby enemies.

Use: Reignite the pilot light to gain 8,239 Intellect for 15 sec. After casting 3 harmful spells, it unleashes a beam dealing 2.4 million Fire damage to your primary target and 199,665 damage to up to 5 enemies in its path. (2 Min Cooldown)
